{"tid":2513953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"魔迷示威闖球場致比賽改期 曼聯或被判輸","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:20:45.000Z","uid":186,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"27281d6b6af46de684393cec9df9480fcc64e7bb","tid":2513953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"曼聯周日對利物浦的英超賽事因為主隊球迷示威並有球迷闖進球場而最終要改期，英國《鏡報》報道，曼聯有可能會受到處分被判輸球。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《鏡報》指英超賽會已就事件展開調查，並正詢問逾200名球迷是如何進入球場。由於迷輕易違反新冠肺炎疫情的防疫規定，曼聯的保安措施正受到仔細審查。根據英足總規章第8.3.4條，如發現對利物浦的比賽未能如期進行曼聯是有過錯，利物浦有機會獲得3分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210503/AMJUVMZSUVFNJEDSI2QLXZJZWY/?fbclid=IwAR0Nrm9vqIR_Khc10QxheAsKd4lpgjzRnn_EgIA_6DLxCQctkNr6qZlV5yQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210503%2FAMJUVMZSUVFNJEDSI2QLXZJZWY%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Nrm9vqIR_Khc10QxheAsKd4lpgjzRnn_EgIA_6DLxCQctkNr6qZlV5yQ&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGteL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=0abb2556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210503%2FAMJUVMZSUVFNJEDSI2QLXZJZWY%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Nrm9vqIR_Khc10QxheAsKd4lpgjzRnn_EgIA_6DLxCQctkNr6qZlV5yQ&h=fe372494\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210503/AMJUVMZSUVFNJEDSI2QLXZJZWY/?fbclid=IwAR0Nrm9vqIR_Khc10QxheAsKd4lpgjzRnn_EgIA_6DLxCQctkNr6qZlV5yQ</a>"},{"pid":"1a7e45fddf04d5b2663beda170a1db3b281aef22","tid":2513953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"係真唔係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d7dbcfacd906be1b3ec0bfa6d197a010663c47","tid":2513953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50128e87f461f410225fdc62526ae9d2efb8e